data.title: Frank Castillo: Lupe
data.meta_description: When Frank Castillo moved to LA, he worked his way up at the iconic Los Angeles venue The Comedy Store and was passed as a Paid Regular.
data.text:
When he moved to LA, he worked his way up at the iconic Los Angeles venue The Comedy Store and was passed as a Paid Regular. Frank became a staple of The Comedy Store Roast Battles, and in January of 2017, Frank became the Champion of Roast Battle II on Comedy Central. Frank can be seen in the Showtime documentary The Comedy Store, in Mike Binder’s upcoming feature Halfway To Amarillo. He has two podcasts Buddies and Peak’d supported by Puffco, Punch extracts and Alienlabs.
